               <provenance>According to Additio 1 (written in hand b),
                     the Ms. was commissioned by Gabra Krǝstos. He and his family members are
                     mentioned in supplication formulas throughout Text I-4b. Their names were
                     partly erased and at the beginning of the text replaced (in hand a) with that
                     of Za-Giyorgis and his family members. Za-Giyorgis is also mentioned throughout
                     Text I-4a.</provenance></history>
